  <Properties>
    <contentGrid>
      <Value><![CDATA[{
  "contentData": [
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "f170b29c-338f-4ab8-a5c4-f72c90826f69",
      "key": "19dde93f-81de-4a3e-83de-b31ac5074a30",
      "values": []
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "c345e5ce-768f-47e0-968a-e7859dbe0b07",
      "key": "233b6bf4-e193-4982-95bf-6fc1f1b3493d",
      "values": []
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "d5bfea49-0733-48ff-9ee0-d83c01a4cbf4",
      "key": "96e30ee5-e180-48c2-a01f-f0a633ccab5a",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "What It Does"
        },
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureDescription",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Lets editors hand-pick specific pages to display as a card grid"
        },
        {
          "alias": "richTextContent",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "Layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EThe Internal Links - Selected feature displays a curated set of pages chosen by the content editor using Umbraco\u0027s Multi Node Tree Picker. Unlike the Children variant which auto-discovers pages, this feature gives editors full control over which pages appear and in what order.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe selected pages render as the same responsive Bootstrap card grid used by the Children variant \u2014 each card shows the page\u0027s thumbnail, title, and description with a stretched link making the entire card clickable.\u003C/p\u003E"
          }
        },
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureSummary",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Editors can pick pages from anywhere in the content tree, not just children of the current page."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "d5bfea49-0733-48ff-9ee0-d83c01a4cbf4",
      "key": "504d66ca-c9c8-4524-851b-18b63b9dee94",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "How It Works"
        },
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureDescription",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "A Multi Node Tree Picker property with the same card rendering as Internal Links - Children"
        },
        {
          "alias": "richTextContent",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "blocks": {
              "contentData": [],
              "settingsData": [],
              "expose": [],
              "Layout": {}
            },
            "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EThe view reads the \u003Ccode\u003ELinks\u003C/code\u003E property \u2014 a Multi Node Tree Picker configured to allow selecting multiple content nodes. The selected items are cast to \u003Ccode\u003EWebPage\u003C/code\u003E using ModelsBuilder\u0027s strongly-typed model, giving access to \u003Ccode\u003EPageTitle\u003C/code\u003E, \u003Ccode\u003EPageDescription\u003C/code\u003E, and \u003Ccode\u003EPageThumbnail\u003C/code\u003E.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThis feature shares the same view file (\u003Ccode\u003EfeatureInternalLinks.cshtml\u003C/code\u003E) with a simple card rendering pattern. The cards use Bootstrap\u0027s CSS Grid with responsive column classes: full width on mobile, 2 columns at md, and 3 columns at lg.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPage thumbnails are rendered using \u003Ccode\u003EGetCropUrl(width: 480)\u003C/code\u003E for optimised image sizes. The card uses Bootstrap\u0027s \u003Ccode\u003Eshadow\u003C/code\u003E and \u003Ccode\u003Estretched-link\u003C/code\u003E utilities for hover effects and full-card clickability.\u003C/p\u003E"
          }
        },
        {
          "alias": "featurePropertyFeatureSummary",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "This feature shares its view with Internal Links - Children, so the card layout is consistent across both."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "c4b3a613-0d2c-4470-8d06-f7efea52d6e0",
      "key": "e1221c97-964b-476c-b392-310c0fb4df7a",
